    "data": [
        {
            "title": "海關截獲往天津走私貨櫃 陶藝品掩飾逾$7000萬電子零件",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海關截獲往天津走私貨櫃 陶藝品掩飾逾$7000萬電子零件\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5533fd7296ab36025c815c251165c731/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041616024957941.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海關截獲往天津走私貨櫃 陶藝品掩飾逾$7000萬電子零件</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港海關近日偵破一宗遠洋船大型走私案，關員在一艘駛往天津貨輪中，揭發走私犯透過貨櫃走私大量如電腦顯示卡、電路板等昂貴電子零件，並利用陶瓷工藝品作掩飾。涉案貨物市值逾7000萬港元，若成功走私可逃稅700萬元。\n\n</p>\n<p>海關港口及海域科貨櫃貨物檢查組署理高級督察黎子康表示，今年4月4日海關跨部門聯合打擊走私，抽查一個前往天津、申報載有陶瓷工藝品的40呎海運貨櫃。關員X光檢查貨櫃後，發現貨櫃內部深淺不一，中間及深處的貨物的密度與形態，顯著與陶瓷工藝品不同。基於上述疑點，海關相信貨櫃收藏走私貨物，遂將案件移交海關有組織罪案調查科跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198597/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關展示涉案證物。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4eeeb5d30692b86ac07cd81fc7c247f8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關展示涉案證物。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198596/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉案貨櫃外圍（藍框）為陶藝品，中間及深處（紅框）則為走私電子零件。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/057b47b883c46b3e01bacfd4c47e0f75/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_150807713_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案貨櫃外圍（藍框）為陶藝品，中間及深處（紅框）則為走私電子零件。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198593/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"走私犯利用陶藝品掩飾貴價電子零件。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b0d414c4ba211f55996c419ce4923cc/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        走私犯利用陶藝品掩飾貴價電子零件。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198592/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8f2b6627d276d933814b6ac975c86f8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198604/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c0edbc02c529ceb9bc65ff12ebb59e3/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198591/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉案貨品總市值逾7000萬元。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4a170da39ec7a8c12dba68923687df7/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案貨品總市值逾7000萬元。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198590/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/532bc2cc8734286dba04a148cd94bd13/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198589/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3f703e18206d58c8924562b3bace0aa8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_143318550_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>海關有組織罪案調查科特別調查第一組調查主任胡雪兒續指，關員調查貨櫃，發現外圍貨物為陶藝品，走私貨物則被掩飾於深處，包括電腦配件、集成電路、光碟機及電路板等，市值逾7000萬港元。海關提到，內地對上述物品需求殷切，因而吸引不法之徒走私，並利用已解散公司名義登記寄件以規避追查。若該批貨物偷運成功，可逃稅約700萬港元。\n\n</p>\n<p>案件仍在調查中，不排除後續拘捕行動。海關提醒，走私屬嚴重罪行，根據《進出口條例》，任何人輸入或輸出未列艙單貨物，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款200萬元及監禁7年，市民切勿以身試法。如發現懷疑走私活動，可致電海關24小時熱線182 80 80，或透過舉報罪案專用電郵帳戶（<a class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"a6c5d4cfcbc3d4c3d6c9d4d2e6c5d3d5d2c9cbd588c1c9d088cecd\" href=\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\">[email protected]</a>）舉報。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198598/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海關有組織罪案調查科特別調查第一組調查主任胡雪兒（左），及港口及海域科貨櫃貨物檢查組署理高級督察黎子康（右）講述行動詳情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6ea1d34a7a46d35684d32086738b4ad3/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250416_150807713_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海關有組織罪案調查科特別調查第一組調查主任胡雪兒（左），及港口及海域科貨櫃貨物檢查組署理高級督察黎子康（右）講述行動詳情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064272/即時-港聞-海關截獲往天津走私貨櫃-陶藝品掩飾逾-7000萬電子零件",
